The uses for table skirting are almost limitless. Registration tables, buffet lines, meetings, weddings, banquets. Any function you plan that uses tables- plan to use skirting! Further coordinate your skirting presentations by using matching table toppers or throw covers.
A durable flame retardant treatment during fabric manufacturing, and all are machine washable/dryable for easy care.
Knitted Twill Fabric Pattern.
100% Polyester.

The uses for table skirting are almost limitless. Registration tables, buffet lines, meetings, weddings, banquets. Any function you plan that uses tables- plan to use skirting! Further coordinate your skirting presentations by using matching table toppers or throw covers.
A durable flame retardant treatment during fabric manufacturing, and all are machine washable/dryable for easy care. Visa™ Fabric. 100% Polyester.

The uses for table skirting are almost limitless. Registration tables, buffet lines, meetings, weddings, banquets. Any function you plan that uses tables- plan to use skirting! Further coordinate your skirting presentations by using matching table toppers or throw covers.

The uses for table skirting are almost limitless. Registration tables, buffet lines, meetings, weddings, banquets. Any function you plan that uses tables- plan to use skirting! Further coordinate your skirting presentations by using matching table toppers or throw covers.
A durable flame retardant treatment during fabric manufacturing, and all are machine washable/dryable for easy care. Visa™ Fabric. 100% Polyester.
